o|title=\u0412\u0435\u043d\u0435\u0446\u0438\u0458\u0430 \u0438 \u0421\u0440\u0431\u0438 \u0443 \u0414\u0430\u043b\u043c\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0458\u0438 \u0443 XVIII \u0432\u0435\u043a\u0443|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-LdBAAAAYAAJ|year=1984|publisher=\u041f\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0432\u0435\u0442\u0430}}\n* {{cite book|last=Ja\u010dov|first=Marko|title=Srbi u mleta\u010dko-turskim ratovima u XVII veku|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vMM2AAAAMAAJ|year=1990|publisher=Sveti arhijerejski sinod Srpske pravoslavne crkve|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Kresti\u0107|first1=Vasilije|last2=Milosavljevi\u0107|first2=Margot|title=History of the Serbs in Croatia and Slavonia 1848\u20131914|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-ZRpAAAAMAAJ|year=1997|publisher=Beogradski izdava\u010dko-grafi\u010dki zavod}}\n* {{cite book|last=Kresti\u0107|first=Vasilije|title=\u0418\u0441\u0442\u043e\u0440\u0438\u0458\u0430 \u0421\u0440\u0431\u0430 \u0443 \u0425\u0440\u0432\u0430\u0442\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0458 \u0438 \u0421\u043b\u0430\u0432\u043e\u043d\u0438\u0458\u0438 1848\u20131914|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CBKCpwAACAAJ|year=2010|publisher=Zavod za Ud\u017ebenike|isbn=978-86-17-17047-7}}\n* {{cite book|last=Leutloff-Grandits|first=Carolin|title=Claiming Ownership in Postwar Croatia: The Dynamics of Property Relations and Ethnic Conflict in the Knin Region|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QfK3q9vSeOMC|year=2006|publisher=LIT Verlag M\u00fcnster|isbn=978-3-8258-8049-1}}\n* {{cite book|last=Mila\u0161|first=Nikodim|authorlink=Nikodim Mila\u0161|title=Pravoslavna Dalmacija : istorijski pregled|location=Novi Sad|publisher=A. Pajevi\u0107a|year=1901|url=https://archive.org/details/pravoslavnadalma00mila |language=sr}} {{PD-icon}}\n* {{cite book|last=Mileusni\u0107|first=Slobodan|title=Spiritual Genocide: A survey of destroyed, damaged and desecrated churches, monasteries and other church buildings during the war 1991\u20131995 (1997)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id